Several fishing spots can be found in the Ruins of Camdozaal, next to the Preparation Table and the Offering Altar in the ruins and near the bridge in the mine.

These spots give access to raw guppy, raw cavefish, raw tetra, and members can fish raw catfish, raw cave eel and raw slimy eel. Of these, the three lower levelled fish can be caught with a small fishing net, the two higher levelled fish can be caught with a big fishing net and the two eels can be caught with a fishing rod and fishing bait.
